0,"dislike":6,"score":34,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-20T15:03:48.000Z","msg":"佢住獨立房？唔方係。就算獨立房都有聲<br />\n<br />\n探病時間咁多人。d職員又其實個個望住晒。點做到㗎"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-20T15:08:06.000Z","msg":"武肺停左探病好耐啦"},{"pid":"ba0af518c23f5f1a37f12fca74cc362ae4cb50d0","tid":2373621,"uid":73991,"like":26,"dislike":3,"score":23,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-20T15:08:39.000Z","msg":"東星駱駝<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9495883776e3fb88186f7017e4df763f7b44481d","tid":2373621,"uid":294121,"like":30,"dislike":27,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-20T15:09:55.000Z","msg":"係咪無俾利是醫生護士<br />\n前排就心口插左把刀"},{"pid":"9124ed1583130c2a40b146b10c3e00470d7bd037","tid":2373621,"uid":364798,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-20T15:11:06.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3dc11a50ed997bc8a38bd5696de8c5deec021225","tid":2373621,"uid":58335,"like":26,"dislike":0,"score":26,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-20T15:12:44.000Z","msg":"上次葛量洪醫院又係類似咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"007a0802a374a89daf993a91c44f1504b5204add","tid":2373621,"uid":50088,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-20T15:14:10.000Z","msg":"就算自殘都搵唔倒把刀啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n唔通搵食飯把膠刀咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b836e9193610c992b34ed0c0e36e1f4c078e5084","tid":2373621,"uid":44209,"like":6,"dislike":7,"score":-1,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2021-01-20T15:15:25.000Z","msg":"伊利沙伯醫院發生病人自殺案，今日（20日）下午4時許，警方接報伊利沙伯醫院職員報案，指病房一名68歲姓冼的男病人於床上昏迷，頸及胸部受傷，身旁有一把22厘米長的生果刀，男子其後證實傷重不治。警方在現場沒有檢獲遺書，調查後相信男子曾經傷害自己，案件列作自殺。<br />\n<br />\n據了解，死者患有血癌，早前由內地回港，其後入院治療，今日於下午3時許被發現於病房內昏迷，疑曾用刀鎅頸及插胸。<br />\n<br />\n伊院發言人表示，病人患白血病，去年12月24日因氣促及發燒而前往急症室求診，隨後入住醫院內科病房。病人入院後經評估認為情緒沒有異樣，院方一直為其提供適切治療。今午3時30分，當醫生檢視病人的臨床情況時，發現病人頸部及身上有多處刀傷，醫護人員立即為病人止血，惟病人情況轉差，醫護人員隨即進行心肺復蘇，並通知病人家屬，病人最終於下午4時40分不治。<br />\n<br />\n發言人指醫院對事件感到難過，向家屬致以深切慰問，並會盡力為家屬提供所需協助，院方亦已透過早期事故通報系統向醫院管理局總辦事處通報，並會成立根源分析委員會調查事件經過並於8星期內提交報告。有關個案已轉交死因裁判官跟進。"},{"pid":"185f6087527ceff6712346014482cf307760d4c8","tid":2373621,"uid":47658,"like":5,"dislike":90,"score":-85,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-20T15:16:08.000Z","msg":"手足<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"354a5eb3e16391414b3870275189d5b9e4131991","tid":2373621,"uid":206594,"like":20,"dislike":0,"score":20,"quote":{"pid":"539040dd09e915ba8e1dcb88f0d04761ef4432be","tid":2373621,"uid":117837,"like":62,"dislike":2,"score":60,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2021-01-20T14:59:00.000Z","msg":"咩年代 仲有人劈友<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-20T15:16:20.000Z","msg":"呢排深水埗成日劈"},{"pid":"bceaf9c87984b50ca705d1a2d05512c1b43b878a","tid":2373621,"uid":3122,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-20T15:16:39.000Z","msg":"入醫院先係自殺<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9aa63884e03f90500007e5a2e35692ecd322faa0","tid":2373621,"uid":34241,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"354a5eb3e16391414b3870275189d5b9e4131991","tid":2373621,"uid":206594,"like":20,"dislike":0,"score":20,"quote":{"pid":"539040dd09e915ba8e1dcb88f0d04761ef4432be","tid":2373621,"uid":117837,"like":62,"dislike":2,"score":60,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2021-01-20T14:59:00.000Z","msg":"咩年代 仲有人劈友<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmo