"replyTime":"2021-01-20T15:55:08.000Z","msg":"隊自己好撚痛<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3e628870b852b2087a596e867dd4b923f458fe36","tid":2373621,"uid":38164,"like":11,"dislike":0,"score":11,"quote":{"pid":"185f6087527ceff6712346014482cf307760d4c8","tid":2373621,"uid":47658,"like":5,"dislike":90,"score":-85,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-20T15:16:08.000Z","msg":"手足<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-20T15:57:44.000Z","msg":"你老母係支足呀 屌你老母<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0a47a5aada44e48811c91d01e890f5a77a39612b","tid":2373621,"uid":188,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-20T15:57:54.000Z","msg":"要自殺都唔會專登入病房先自殺啦<br />\n貪你日日有人巡房見到咩 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance3.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />係間屋仔死幾日都無人知啦"},{"pid":"09e39640d80c690ed360636826e79273f08c3365","tid":2373621,"uid":76804,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-20T15:58:28.000Z","msg":"自殺插胸𠝹頸<br />\n就算好大決心都唔會做得出啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}